snippet: Tarik Black scored 19 points on perfect shooting in his final game at Allen Fieldhouse, and No. 8 Kansas managed just fine without injured center Joel Embiid in an 82-57 romp over Texas Tech on Wednesday night....

headline.print_headline: No. 8 Jayhawks Roll Over Texas Tech, 82-57
headline.main: No. 8 Jayhawks Roll Over Texas Tech, 82-57

lead_paragraph: Tarik Black scored 19 points on perfect shooting in his final game at Allen Fieldhouse, and No. 8 Kansas managed just fine without injured center Joel Embiid in an 82-57 romp over Texas Tech on Wednesday night.
